import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['delay'] = pd.to_datetime(data['delay'], format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', errors='ignore')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', kde=True)
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%H')
    ax = sns.scatterplot(x='distance', y='delay', data=data)
    ax.set_xlabel('Distance (miles)')
    ax.set_ylabel('Delay (minutes)')
    ax.set_title('Is there a correlation between flight distance and delay time?', wrap=True)
    ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    ax.tick_params(axis='x', rotation=90)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['delay'] = pd.to_numeric(data['delay'], errors='ignore')
    ax = sns.barplot(x=data['delay'], y=data.index)
    ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.title('What is the average delay time for flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.axvline(x=data['delay'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Mean: {data["delay"].mean():.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%H')
    ax = sns.lineplot(x='time', y=data.index, data=data)
    ax.set_xlabel('Time of Day')
    ax.set_ylabel('Number of Flights')
    ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=90)
    plt.title('What is the busiest time of day for flights?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
